    "Details": "A newer variant produced by VEST for the Solaris arenas, the 3T uses a small shield like the J3, though at the cost of armor. This variant is produced solely for the arenas, as it has too little armor for actual combat.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Short</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 0.99</color></b>",
